Salesforce Summer â€™24 Release Notes

Revenue Lifecycle Management now supports custom field mapping for operations such as quote creation, order creation, asset creation, asset update, and contract creation. Add custom fields to Revenue Lifecycle Management objects to meet your business goals.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management and Product Configurator are enabled.

With support for custom field mapping, the values are passed from object to object as your transaction moves from one stage to the other. For example, add a unique Installation Date field, that can be configured in Product Configurator, modified in Quote and Order Capture, and assetized in Asset Lifecycle.
title: Enhance Revenue Lifecycle Management with Custom Field Mapping
